entry.title: Updates on My Squidoo Lens
entry.content: Apparently the PR update have left my squidoo lens with a PR3. Lately I have been working on my lens a bit keeping it fresh and stay on top 100 on the SEO category. I have converting some old blog post and writing some new ones. I like to see how much I have made form my lens from September onwards. Right now Squidoo only reports up to August earnings. I have also delete away all my other lens so the sole and surviving one looks more creditable. If interested in making money from squidoo, you check out some of my older articles on them.
